dct_description_sm: United States. Army Map Service. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4274. North Decimal Degree 33.883333. South Decimal Degree 33.883333. Source: Gabes 1:50,000, Service geographique de l'Armee 1933; Intelligence reports 1941-42. In lower right margin: Drawn by War Office 1942.
